Yours,
Kay

`test_reading_after_writing_with_load_schema` work fine when `Parent.avsc` has only on Child Type field(Defined by `Child.asvc`).But when `Parent.avsc` has multiple  Child type, an exception will be raised:`TypeError: 'dict' object cannot be interpreted as an integer`。

Use schemas bellow can reappear this bug:
Parent.avsc
```
{
  "type":"record",
  "name":"Parent",
  "fields":[
    {
      "name": "child",
      "type": "Child"
    },
    {
      "name": "anotherChild",
      "type": "AnotherChild"
    }
  ]
}
```
Child.avsc
```
